{"tid":1564668,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何超瓊聯合國發言﹕年輕人被煽動犯罪　 市民是最大受害者","createTime":"2019-09-13T00:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:08:56.000Z","uid":147956,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c56de381799ae5e5e259cd6449a05546bd67543d","tid":1564668,"uid":147956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rs74nzc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRs74nzc.jpg&h=98209667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合國人權理事會第42次會議周三（11日）在日內瓦召開。香港各界婦女聯合協進會主席何超瓊在會上發言，她譴責示威者日益暴力的行為，稱許多年輕人離家出走成為前線暴徒，被煽動犯罪。她強調不容許孩子被利用，呼籲國際社會譴責組織示威者，表明暴力極端主義只會給香港留下無法彌補的傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，自6月9日至今，已有130場示威活動，當中110宗以暴力及非法行為收場，令過百間小企業關閉及不少人失業。她指出，普通市民是最大受害者，家庭分化，數量驚人的年輕人離家出走成為前線暴徒，被煽動從事犯罪活動。<br />\n<br />\n何超瓊續說，各年齡層孩子在校及網絡，被灌輸反政府及仇視警察思想，並舉行大規模罷課，那些拒絕參與的學童，尤是警察子女，會受到身體及網絡惡意恐嚇及欺凌。"},{"pid":"c0bdb454776929247300379bac52217da2bb0b59","tid":1564668,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:54:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9c8447abb8c09b46faa1700c8a4965b828d1dc20","tid":1564668,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:08:56.000Z","msg":"[行動]913全港和你慶中秋終極版!<br />\n- 分享